description:
NOTE: Audio drops out at 38:10, but returns within 30 seconds. Several PDF copies of Covert Action Information Bulletin are available, or free, at our archive.org collection: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

For Lou Wolf on Alternative Views TV: https://archive.org/details/AV_153_154_155-COVERT_ACTION
For Bill Schaap and Lou Wolf: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ1YcFpInEs

Contains telephone interview with William Schaap and Louis Wolf of the C.A.I.B. who discuss the proposed intelligence protection legislation. 

See more at: http://pacificaradioarchives.org/recording/kz0857#sthash.l74E8uYj.dpuf
